<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4504577>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 3. Molecular affiliation of M. sedimensis new species, and M. hijauensis new species, based on ML analysis of the CO1 DNA barcode sequence, with Pontodrilus litoralis as the out-group. Bar represents the number of nucleotide substitutions per site. Codes before the species name are the museum reference number, whilst those afterwards are the GenBank sequence accession numbers, Jeratthitikul et al. (2017)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4504577/files/figure.png" .

